+## Overview
+
+Across 30 orders, total revenue was $7,154.44 (`data/sales.csv:2-31`). With an even order count, the $190.00 and $219.89 middle values yield a $204.95 median (`data/sales.csv:2-31`).
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget generated $2,392.00, or 33.43% of revenue, 12.89% more than Widget's $2,118.94 (`data/sales.csv:2-31`). Doohickey produced $1,513.00 and Sprocket $1,130.50 (`data/sales.csv:2-31`).
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North generated $2,176.35; East $1,830.79; South $1,732.48; and West $1,414.82 (`data/sales.csv:2-31`). North's 30.42% share was 53.83% above West's revenue (`data/sales.csv:2-31`).
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget stock: it generated $2,392.00, 33.43% of revenue (`data/sales.csv:2-31`).
+- Study North's 30.42% share; its revenue exceeded West's by 53.83% (`data/sales.csv:2-31`).
+- Test Sprocket promotions: its $1,130.50 revenue was 47.26% of Gadget revenue (`data/sales.csv:2-31`).
